#: 6d16dd9a8fbb4ea2a3e6ace3ec972173
msgid "``policy.Ask`` - ask the user about whether to execute a given action"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/services/qrexec-internals.rst:345
#: d7a0b73181cf4c72a9043ec08c16e0f3
msgid "``policy.Notify`` - notify the user about an action."
msgstr ""

